I wanted to tell you so badly,
I came back as fast as I could.

473
00:23:14,828 --> 00:23:17,030
But, there weren't any
direct flights.

474
00:23:17,130 --> 00:23:20,400
[TAMAKI GRUFFLY]
I want to hug you.

475
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,836
To hug me? Or Yuuki?

476
00:23:24,204 --> 00:23:26,439
[TAMAKI]
Both of you.

477
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:28,775
[MIDORI]
Yeah...

478
00:23:28,875 --> 00:23:31,044
I hope the day comes
that you can...

479
00:23:31,144 --> 00:23:32,946
Tamaki.

480
00:23:42,656 --> 00:23:44,424
[ANZAI & TSUKASA]
DEVILS' LINE,

481
00:23:44,525 --> 00:23:45,792
Line 9,

482
00:23:45,892 --> 00:23:47,561
"Command."

